Plugin Name: WIT Automatic Link Exchange
Plugin URI: http://www.worldit.info
Description: WIT Automatic Link Exchange is a Wordpress plugin which has an automated link exchange system. The main features are the possibility to create weekly and monthly charts. This plugin is trying to sustain link exchange actions. The plugin has an automated monitoring system for links. Rankings are organized according to the refferers, votes etc. Rankings are beeing reset, although history charts are kepy in the archive. 
Version: 0.1
Author: Avadanei Andrei
Author URI: http://www.worldit.info/

